<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1075.55862.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Intersection of vein R 1 with vein C (white), distance between apices of veins R 1 and R 2 + 3 and apices of veins R 2 + 3 and R 4 + 5 (blue), distal vein R 4 + 5 (pink) and setosity of proximal ventral half of vein C (red). A Romaleosyrphus bigoti sp. nov. B Sphecomyia weismani (Moran) C Criorhina bubulcus (Walker)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/619714" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1075.55862.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Romaleosyrphus dorsal habitus A: Romaleosyrphus arctophiloides B: Romaleosyrphus vockerothi sp. nov. C: Romaleosyrphus soletluna sp. nov. rufous morph D: Romaleosyrphus soletluna sp. nov. black morph E: Romaleosyrphus villosus F. Romaleosyrphus bigoti sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/619715" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1075.55862.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Romaleosyrphus lateral habitus A Romaleosyrphus arctophiloides B Romaleosyrphus vockerothi sp. nov. C Romaleosyrphus soletluna sp. nov. rufous morph D Romaleosyrphus soletluna sp. nov. black morph E Romaleosyrphus villosus F Romaleosyrphus bigoti sp. nov." ;
